Once recorded the VAT settlement, the plafond amount still remaining will be reported automatically in the following month.

To print the VAT Plafond choose the relevant option in Calc. reg and VAT payment:

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000625-0/27VatManagement-en.png"><br>

