|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| Starting from BC17, if the **"Starting Date" is changed,** compared to that proposed by the system, for technical reasons, the **Preview may not display the correct dates** . We therefore **suggest to always Print or Print in pdf.**  |